'''CD28受体家族'''（{{lang-en|CD28 family receptors}}）是一类表达在[[免疫细胞|免疫细胞]][[細胞表面受體|表面的受體]]，CD28家族也是[[免疫球蛋白超家族|免疫球蛋白超家族]]的一员<ref name = "Arch_2012">{{cite book | first1 = Robert H. | last1 = Arch | first2 = Jonathan M | last2 = Green | chapter = Chapter 16: Costimulatory molecules in T-cell activation and transplantation: Section 2: The CD28 receptor family | pages = 292–8 | editor-last1=Burlingham |editor-first1=William J. |editor-last2=Wilkes |editor-first2=David S. |title=Immunobiology of Organ Transplantation |date=2012 |publisher=Springer US |location=Boston, MA |isbn=978-1-4419-8999-4 | chapter-url = https://books.google.com/books?id=SH3TBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA292 }}</ref> 。

家族的两个成员，[[CD28|CD28]]和[[CD278|ICOS]]，能作为[[T细胞|T细胞]]的阳性激活受体，另外三个[[BTLA|BTLA]]<ref name="Carreno_2003">{{cite journal | vauthors = Carreno BM, Collins M | title = BTLA: a new inhibitory receptor with a B7-like ligand | journal = Trends in Immunology | volume = 24 | issue = 10 | pages = 524–7 | date = October 2003 | pmid = 14552835 | doi = 10.1016/j.it.2003.08.005 }}</ref>、[[CTLA-4|CTLA-4]]和[[PD-1|PD-1]]则起抑制作用<ref name = "Arch_2012" />，CD28家族受体的[[配體_(生物化學)|配体]]通常为[[B7蛋白质家族|B7蛋白质家族]]<ref name="Carreno_2002">{{cite journal | vauthors = Carreno BM, Collins M | title = The B7 family of ligands and its receptors: new pathways for costimulation and inhibition of immune responses | journal = Annual Review of Immunology | volume = 20 | issue =  | pages = 29–53 | date = 2002 | pmid = 11861596 | doi = 10.1146/annurev.immunol.20.091101.091806 }}</ref>。

CD28受体家族在T细胞的发育和增殖中起作用<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Wakamatsu E, Omori H, Ohtsuka S, Ogawa S, Green JM, Abe R | title = Regulatory T cell subsets are differentially dependent on CD28 for their proliferation | journal = Molecular Immunology | volume = 101 | pages = 92–101 | date = September 2018 | pmid = 29909367 | doi = 10.1016/j.molimm.2018.05.021 }}</ref>，增强来自[[T细胞受体|T细胞受体]]（TCR）的信号，以刺激免疫反应<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Morin SO, Giroux V, Favre C, Bechah Y, Auphan-Anezin N, Roncagalli R, Mège JL, Olive D, Malissen M, Nunès JA | display-authors = 6 | title = In the absence of its cytosolic domain, the CD28 molecule still contributes to T cell activation | journal = Cellular and Molecular Life Sciences | volume = 72 | issue = 14 | pages = 2739–48 | date = July 2015 | pmid = 25725801 | pmc = 4826669 | doi = 10.1007/s00018-015-1873-7 }}</ref>，以及对[[调节性T细胞|调节性T细胞]]的[[抗炎性|抗炎反应]]。

